# .dockerignore - Exclude files from Docker build context
#
# Purpose:
# - Speed up builds by excluding unnecessary files
# - Reduce final image size
# - Prevent secrets from being copied into images
# - Avoid cache invalidation from temporary files
#
# How it works:
# - Files matching these patterns are NOT sent to Docker daemon during build
# - Similar to .gitignore syntax
# - Reduces build context size, making builds faster

# ============================================================================
# Version Control
# ============================================================================
